metadata.description: Persona Lamps is a collection of 4,444 LAMP NFTs with over 100 variations and countless combination of traits that each represents the light generated throughout the NFTuniverse. Each Persona Lamp wears a type of clothing that represents their current or past occupations, with the traits hovering around them as their occupation or interests. Your Persona Lamp will also grant you access to future events and expansions! Visit us here! https://www.personalamps.com/
metadata.name: Persona Lamp #1
